caption.text:
Today I got my first ever Amiibo!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Not only is it the awakening of a beautiful collection but can we just look at how adorable this wee Link is! A very good first Amiibo me thinks.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
I feel torn about whether to open him up! It's stupid I know but he looks so cool in his printed box... but I want to use him - AH DILEMMA (not really, I'll open him when I stop being silly).
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Who else has had a go on the brand new release of Link's Awakening? It's so charming. The music is wonderful and all of my concerns over its art direction when it was first announced are smushed - it's gorgeous! Where are you up to on Link's Awakening? I've already claimed a Yoshi Doll from the claw machine and started the Tail Dungeon!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Also, my holiday was wonderful! I saw so many beautiful sights and got to spend days exploring with my beautiful wife and in-laws. Happy to be home though! Feel like I need time off after my holiday - I'M KNACKERED!

Después de que Nintendo Francia anunciara hace unos días la prohibición de Hero en torneos de Super Smash Bros. en el país, hoy decidieron revocar el "ban". Aquí el mensaje que dieron: "Estamos armonizando estas reglas en toda Europa para asegurarnos de que ninguna comunidad o país esté en desventaja cuando compita en la final "pan-Europea" el próximo año. En términos de futuros lanzamientos de luchadores, crearemos reglamentaciones más detalladas para nuestros organizadores de torneos, para asegurarnos de mantener un campo de juego nivelado a través de la elegibilidad constante de luchadores en toda Europa ". #nintendo #supersmashbros #hero #nintendoswitch #videogames #francia

🚨 NEW EP! 🚨 This week, we grab our green tights, and polish our swords as we dive into THE LEGEND OF ZELDA: LINK'S AWAKENING on the Nintendo Switch! Can this remake of the 1993 GameBoy classic hold up to our 2019 gaming sensibilities, or can we not handle the fetch quests and backtracking? Also, you know we've got a heaping helping of Geek News for you: Is Jonah Hill joining the upcoming Batman film as a very iconic villain? A television return of a classic Superman has us very excited! Do you need to remember to duck and cover when you see the Joker film? Sony gives us lots of reasons so hand them all our money with their annual State of Play! All that, plus: WonderRob rants about Kryptonite, Shoff goes for the Optimus Prime impression record, and we both find out who the REAL sex pervert is. So sit back, relax, and thanks for tuning in... SAME GEEK TIME, SAME GEEK CHANNEL!

preview_comments.text: If a developer doesn’t say their game has gone gold, don’t buy it!

caption.text:
<<<SWIPE LEFT<<< ‘Death Stranding’ will be released November 8, and today the game has officially gone gold.⁣
⁣
Going gold in case you don’t know, means the game is fully developed and is ready to be shipped for release.⁣
⁣
In other news, a listing for the ‘Death Stranding’ edition PS4 Pro on GAME UK's website shows that a PS Plus subscription is not required on the console's box. ⁣
⁣
The game will use a light online system - like  in ‘Dark Souls’ and ‘NieR: Automata’ - where you can see traces and tracks left behind by other players in the game's world. ⁣
⁣
It will also have a "like” mechanic where you can rate objects other players have left behind.⁣
⁣
With just over a month for ‘Death Stranding’ to be released, tomorrow is almost in our hands.⁣
